## üß™ Option 1: ClickFix Simulation (SAFE)

### üìÑ `clickfix_simulation.txt`

```powershell
# ==============================
# SAFE CLICKFIX SIMULATION
# ==============================
# This script simulates:
# - Clipboard abuse
# - PowerShell execution
# - Fake CAPTCHA workflow
# NO malware, NO exfiltration

Write-Output "[SIMULATION] Fake CAPTCHA verification started"

Start-Sleep -Seconds 2

Write-Output "[SIMULATION] User copied command from clipboard"
Write-Output "[SIMULATION] Executing PowerShell via cmd.exe"

$log = "$env:TEMP\clickfix_simulation.log"

Add-Content $log "Fake CAPTCHA executed at $(Get-Date)"
Add-Content $log "Simulated mshta / powershell execution"
Add-Content $log "No malicious activity performed"

Write-Output "[SIMULATION] Execution complete"
```

Triggers:

* PowerShell execution
* LOLBin behavior
* Process creation logs
* EDR detections

