## üß™ Option 2: Fake Stealer Simulation

### üìÑ `stealer_behavior_sim.txt`

```powershell
# ==============================
# SAFE STEALER SIMULATION
# ==============================
# Simulates credential harvesting behavior
# WITHOUT accessing real credentials

Write-Output "[SIMULATION] Enumerating fake data"

$fakeData = @(
  "username=testuser",
  "browser=Chrome",
  "os=Windows 11",
  "ip=127.0.0.1"
)

$path = "$env:TEMP\stealer_sim_output.txt"
$fakeData | Out-File $path

Write-Output "[SIMULATION] Data collected:"
Get-Content $path

Write-Output "[SIMULATION] No data exfiltrated"
```

Simulates:

* File creation
* ‚ÄúData collection‚Äù
* Disk artifacts
* EDR behavior analytics

