## üß™ Option 3: Fake C2 Beacon (LOCALHOST ONLY)

### üìÑ `c2_beacon_sim.txt`

```powershell
# ==============================
# SAFE C2 BEACON SIMULATION
# ==============================
# NEVER contacts real servers

$server = "http://127.0.0.1:8080"
$log = "$env:TEMP\c2_simulation.log"

Add-Content $log "Beacon attempt to $server at $(Get-Date)"

Write-Output "[SIMULATION] Beacon sent to localhost"
```

Simulates:

* Network connections
* IDS / NDR alerts
* Beacon timing patterns

